tasks.title: Test
tasks.description: Complete the full redesign of the dashboard user interface, including responsive layout improvements, accessibility fixes, and performance optimization. Ensure the design works smoothly on mobile, tablet, and desktop devices. Add animations for better user experience, refactor old components, and test everything across different browsers. Document all changes clearly so other team members can maintain the code easily in the future.
